# Environment Setup for LLM Integration

## Optional: Google Gemini API

To enable advanced natural language understanding with LLM, set your Gemini API key:

### Windows (PowerShell)
```powershell
$env:GEMINI_API_KEY="AIzaSyCJrmQZvea9dyaPQH1CtJPJILVpsE4VSOQ"
```

### Linux/Mac
```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY="AIzaSyCJrmQZvea9dyaPQH1CtJPJILVpsE4VSOQ"
```

### Get API Key
1. Go to https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
2. Create a new API key
3. Copy and set as environment variable

## Note
The agent works WITHOUT an API key using keyword-based matching. The LLM just enhances understanding and adds conversational memory features.
